Name: Average resolution time of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents within the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Unmatched + Unmatched to Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents compared to Accepted + Wait - User incidents
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents compared to Completed + Resolved incidents
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum duration of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents compared to Accepted + Wait - Vendor incidents
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average time it takes from Unmatched + Unmatched to reach Completed + Closed status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time it takes from Unmatched + Unmatched to reach Completed + In Call status
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle time of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents in the context of VINST system operations
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time for Unmatched + Unmatched incidents before transitioning to any other activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of incidents starting with Unmatched + Unmatched and ending with Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time it takes for an incident to move from Unmatched + Unmatched to Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of Unmatched + Unmatched incidents before transitioning to Accepted + Wait - Customer
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
